Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.55,ef_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1274,0)\bord0.125\be1\fsp-0.5\fs35\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFCFCF7&\pos(421,385)}POSLEDNÍ ODPAD TOHOTO SVĚTA —
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.30,ef_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(442,0)\bord0.125\be1\fsp-0.5\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFCFCF7&\pos(278,107)}DOLŮ
